examples.en: Fish is a mainstay of their diet.
She was the mainstay of the team.
He was the mainstay of the organization.
My mother has always been the mainstay of our family.
examples.ru: Моя мама всегда была опорой нашей семьи.

examples.en: Agriculture is still the mainstay of the country's economy.
examples.ru: Сельское хозяйство всё ещё является основой экономики страны.
